Metasoma
. T1 petiolate with spiracle at 0.6 to 0.75 (
Fig. 1
), dorsal carinae absent, dorsolateral carinae indistinct or absent anterior to spiracle, T1 sculpture impunctate, glymma absent (most species), indistinct or present; membranous portion of S1 not or only slightly projecting lateral to sclerotized portion of T1; ovipositor moderately upcurved, dorsal valve thick and rounded apically (
Fig. 1
), overlapping ventral valve laterally.
